contentfulPagePressRelease.title: Qatar Music Academy Celebrates National Day at Qatar Foundation’s Darb El-Saai Tent

childMarkdownRemark.html:
Image 1: A student of Qatar Music Academy, a member of Qatar Foundation for Education, Science and Community Development (QF), performs on stage alongside an instructor at Darb El-Saai.


Image 2: A trio of musicians from Qatar Music Academy perform at Qatar Foundation for Education, Science and Community Development’s (QF) Darb El-Saai tent.


Image 3: Students from Qatar Music Academy perform on percussion instruments at Qatar Foundation for Education, Science and Community Development’s (QF) Darb El-Saai tent.


Image 4: Qatar Music Academy students during a violin recital at Qatar Foundation for Education, Science and Community Development’s (QF) Darb El-Saai tent.
